OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,6,Fthrough the day, but scattered,
OL,7,Fblustery showers continue with some
OL,8,Fwith hail. There will be sunny spells
OL,9,Ftoo, but feeling chilly in the
OL,10,Fnortherly wind with temperatures
OL,11,Fremaining below average for mid-May.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe wind and showers will
OL,14,Fease overnight, becoming mostly dry by
OL,15,Fmorning. Some clear spells developing
OL,16,Funder lighter winds, allowing for a
OL,17,Fchilly end to the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
