OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FThe odd early shower is
OL,6,Fpossible, otherwise a dry day with
OL,7,Flight winds. Cloudy at times, but with
OL,8,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,9,Fless chilly in the lighter winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry with light winds on Saturday. A
OL,13,Fband of showery rain moves east on
OL,14,FSunday. Rain possible later on Monday.
OL,15,FTemperatures returning to near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
